txt.en: 'Good job, my friend. This knowledge is best forgotten.'
The sorceress Brágha Fellwinder has gone to Caivád Sâr, where she intends to teach her fellow Angmarim how to make more of the corrupted Wargs.

'Nasty business was that piece of sorcery. You have done a great deed in keeping the crystals and spells out of the hands of the enemy. Wargs are monstrous enough without being driven mad and having their strength enhanced.'

Brágha Fellwinder has gone to the tower of Caivád Sâr, in central Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat Brágha Fellwinder before she can pass on the knowledge of the crystals and the corruption her spells bring.
Gunvald is in Annâk-khurfu in Elderslade.\n\nReturn to Gunvald.
